==Nagradostiya==
Ande [[Thessaloniki]], [[Greshiya|Yelenestan]], o film, kerdo pe Yelenestan sar "Gadjo Dilo: There are still smiling gypsies" ("Aba si asamaste Romane" pe Romanes) dubisaylo o nagrada ando 41-to [[Thessaloniki Film Festival]] ando 1998to bersh.

